            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_108wh' title='Col. 108WH &mdash; HC Deb 21 March 2001 vol 365 c108WH' name='column_108wh' href='#column_108wh' rel='bookmark'>108WH</a>
            hundreds of thousands if not millions of families. There is nothing that the hon. Lady can say to defend the actions of 18 years of Tory government.
          </p>
